data.description: Nice house that has a large flat yard in the Heart of Beebe. 3 bedrooms with another room that can be a forth. Currently used as a bedroom. Huge laundry room that also shares a full bath. Nice original hardwoods. Spacious Kitchen and dining room. Covered back patio overlooks the large back yard. There is a concrete pad already in place to build you a nice shed. Fridge, washer and dryer stay. Multiple peices of furniture can stay if desired. Needs some TLC and updating. No Stove. Central Heat and air are out and may need replaced. Conventional loan, or Cash only. AS IS. Seller Will not make any repairs.
